library(tidyverse) h=function(t,a,b,d,e) exp(-a*t)*sin(t*b+3)+exp(-d*t)*sin(t*e+1) f=sample(2:3,4,T) d=runif(4,0,0.01) seq(1,80,.0005)%>% data.frame(.,x=h(.,d[1],f[1],d[2],f[2]), y=h(.,d[3],f[3],d[4],f[4]))%>% ggplot(aes(x, y))+geom_path()+theme_void() #rstats pic.twitter.com/scPZ7jfo9m
